item.title: TryHackMe: Overpass
item.description: Here’s my write-up for Overpass, a CTF challenge created by NinjaJc01. Write-up I deployed the box using TryHackMe’s interface and scanned the host using nmap: └─$ nmap -sC -sV 10.10.131.138 -p- Starting Nmap 7.92 ( https://nmap.org ) at 2022-07-08 09:27 EDT Nmap scan report for 10.10.131.138 Host is up (0.059s latency). Not shown: 65533 closed tcp ports (conn-refused) PORT STATE SERVICE VERSION 22/tcp open ssh OpenSSH 7.6p1 Ubuntu 4ubuntu0.3 (Ubuntu Linux; protocol 2.
